annotation.text:
A legendary musician, ''James Louis Johnson's'' career spans over half a century, with countless sessions either as leader or as sideman, performing with most top-bop cats.
His influence is not limited to the "trombone area", and most of his tunes are standards.
''Blue Note'' has very good starters, namely ''The Eminent Jay Jay Johnson'' volumes.
